olive oil
1 packet Totara Tasty Cheddar
1 packet Croissants
1 packet Garlic Aioli
1 packet Shaved Champagne Ham

Preheat oven to 220°C/200°C
fan-forced. Thinly slice
Totara Cheddar cheese. Cut
croissants in half
horizontally.

Spread croissant bases with
garlic aioli and top with
cheese and ham. Top with
croissant tops and place
on an oven tray. Bake until
cheese is melted,
5-8 mins.

Divide croissants between
plates.